`todo sync` pushes issues to an external tracker (GitHub Issues or ClickUp) configured in `.todo.yml` under `sync:`. Run `todo sync --help` for setup and usage.

## Concurrency Control

`todo show <id> --etag-only` → `todo update <id> --if-match "$ETAG" ...`

## GraphQL

`todo query` supports advanced queries/mutations. Use `--help` for syntax, `--schema` for full schema.

```bash
todo query --json '{ issues(filter: { excludeStatus: ["completed", "scrapped"], isBlocked: false }) { id title status type body } }'
todo query --json '{ issue(id: "abc") { title body parent { title } children { id title status } } }'
```
